Interface BoundedStream

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BlockInStream, BufferedBlockInStream, FileInStream, LocalBlockInStream, RemoteBlockInStream, UnderStoreFileInStream

    public interface BoundedStream
    This interface should be implemented by all Tachyon streams which are bounded at a certain byte size.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      long remaining()
      Gets the remaining number of bytes left in the stream, starting at the current position.
